name: Giantess | Concept
description:
For generating really big girls

*4.0 update* Overhauled from scratch
Not sure if its entirely an upgrade, running into the upper limit of separate concepts I can try and shove in without completely frying it

Keywords description:
GTS - Trained on girls surrounded by similar sized buildings

GTScity - Trained on girls surround by a number of relatively smaller buildings

GTSgiga - Trained on girls with vast landscapes, mountains, and urban sprawls

GTSplanet - Trained on girls atop the big blue sphere

GTSspace - Trained on girls floating in the void, only a small blue sphere for company

GTSCramped- Trained on girls trapped in undersized rooms

Looming - Trained to replicate a very low perspective

Stepping - Similar to the last but with a bare foot taking up much of the frame
[Buggy] Stuck to the whims of the model being able to accurately assemble a foot

Rampage - Trained on collapsed buildings to replicate the usual amount of infrastructure damage

Sitting on Building - If she sits on demand, give her a treat


Plays well with most other LoRAs
Recommend 0.8-1 Strength

If you've enjoyed my models, consider leaving a tip.
https://ko-fi.com/leontalon
